Begin the grimoire.

Inquire whispers of "What is your name?" into name.
Inscribe whispers of "Hello".
Inscribe name.

Inquire whispers of "Enter your age:" into ageText.
Transmute ageText into number.
Summon the age with essence of ageText.

If the signs show age greater than 18 then Inscribe whispers of "You are an adult!" otherwise Inscribe whispers of "You are a minor.".

Close the grimoire.